diergo.spring.legacy

Class CustomizingTypeFilter<T extends Member>

  • java.lang.Object
    • diergo.spring.legacy.CustomizingTypeFilter<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SmartBeanDefinitionCustomizer, BeanDefinitionCustomizer, TypeFilter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LegacyBeanMethodFilter, LegacySingletonFieldFilter

    abstract class CustomizingTypeFilter<T extends Member>
extends Object
implements TypeFilter, SmartBeanDefinitionCustomizer
    Support class to combine type filtering, bean definition filtering and customizing as needed by the post processor. A type filter creating bean definitions for visible members declared static on class level.
    See Also:
    MemberPredicates.visible(), MemberPredicates.atClass(), LegacyBeanRegistryPostProcessorBuilder
